snippet.title: Defend from Candyland!
snippet.description:
Take charge of an arboretum arsenal in defense of the land of Eden in "Defend from Candyland!"

Fight fixed waves and endless optional hordes across 60 levels in this tower defense game.

Available on Steam:  https://store.steampowered.com/app/1800480/Defend_from_Candyland/

This video is not sponsored by the developer, but I was offered a key to check it out. Thank you to MI Pixel for the opportunity!
